comment: In 2014, the company switched from the reporting period of July-June to January-December. Therefore, the 2014 reporting period only covers July 2014-December 2014. I added the this to the waste produced from the period July 2013-June2014. Thus, the year given here (2014) covers the period of July2013-December2014. (=3413328+8197000)
